{"tid":988047,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐襲主腦】疑為爭取連任 印尼總統釋放激進教士","createTime":"2019-01-19T17:27:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T19:11:02.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c52d8ff8ccf2035adae6258dbf16941ce42ac9cb","tid":988047,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T17:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190119/large/1547899323_5f78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190119%2Flarge%2F1547899323_5f78.jpg&h=2bd42ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n激進伊斯蘭教士巴希爾（中）(路透社)<br />\n2002年印尼峇里島大爆炸導致逾200人死，被指是事件幕後主腦的激進伊斯蘭教士巴希爾（Abu Bakar Bashir）卻將提早出獄，印尼總統維多多指釋放巴希爾出於人道理由，但外界相信其決定與他部署在4月大選連任有關。<br />\n2002年10月12日，峇里島一間夜店遭「伊斯蘭祈禱團」施放炸彈襲擊，<span style=\"color: red;\">事件202名死者中有11人來自香港</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。80歲的巴希爾被視為激進組織「伊斯蘭祈禱團」（Jemaah Islamiah）的精神領袖，2011年因與蘇門答臘北端二亞齊省（Aceh）一個武裝分子訓練營有關，被判違反反恐法，入獄15年。<br />\n維多多周五表示，釋放巴希爾的首要原因是人道主義，「他是長者，健康狀況也獲考慮」，另稱有安全考慮，但無進一步說明。其競選團隊法律顧問馬亨德拉（Yusril Mahendra）就指巴希爾健康一般，但服刑態度良好，而當局原要求他以放棄激進信仰換取假釋，但維多多最終選擇「尊重」其信仰並放寬假釋條件。<br />\n巴希爾的代表律師亦確認他將獲釋，指他已服刑逾1/3刑期，有資格獲假釋，但巴希爾之前拒絕簽署假釋條件同意書，因他不承認印尼世俗政府的權力，堅稱只向真主負責。<br />\n當局未交代巴希爾從西爪哇衞星城市茂物（Bogor）監獄出冊的具體日期，但巴希爾兒子指他最快周二回家，並為不良於行又無辜的父親獲釋鬆一口氣。<br />\n正爭取連任總統的維多多，被政敵指控向伊斯蘭教士濫告刑事罪行，馬亨德拉指維多多今次決定「可向公眾展示他迫害或以刑事罪名控告教士的說法有誤」。<br />\n路透社/美聯社/美國有線新聞網絡  <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190119/59162132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190119%2F59162132&d=d5f8ptpmWACKIqiBNBA0kP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=431f93af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190119%2F59162132&h=afc1960f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190119/59162132</a>"},{"pid":"7b321e237a8eee99ff6ff4ee1fd62cf56ede4852","tid":988047,"uid":117276,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T17:31:10.000Z","msg":"恐怖份子殺200人竟然唔使槍斃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐15年搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4040a0f9535c099895bcfd940e662a5ff0d75685","tid":988047,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T17:57:27.000Z","msg":"印尼山番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d9ace870a2b043323ddfefb1a36c37a9b0e562","tid":988047,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T01:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bac1d9792abf2d4b93500bc1b4e2f53b39dea87b","tid":988047,"uid":168698,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:34:24.000Z","msg":"始終都係老人家，要體諒要包容<br />\n伊斯蘭教係和平既宗教，他只係少數姐"},{"pid":"f33b2f9bcb4694ef40c314d2930a4c028d5e39fc","tid":988047,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bac1d9792abf2d4b93500bc1b4e2f53b39dea87b","tid":988047,"uid":168698,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:34:24.000Z","msg":"始終都係老人家，要體諒要包容<br />\n伊斯蘭教係和平既宗教，他只係少數姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"#曲"},{"pid":"b5e5b7cf8051981280a959125aabe20605447aa0","tid":988047,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bac1d9792abf2d4b93500bc1b4e2f53b39dea87b","tid":988047,"uid":168698,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T02:34:24.000Z","msg":"始終都係老人家，要體諒要包容<br />\n伊斯蘭教係和平既宗教，他只係少數姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T04:06:41.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教=恐怖份子"},{"pid":"2e8270da5